what_you_do: Elizabeth Johnston facilitates personal and professional transformation through private coaching and a variety of seminars in writing, bodhran, creativity and well-being.
business_focus: Elizabeth Johnston is an online entrepreneur, business coach, and writing professor. She also has a podcast, "Own Your Creativity," where she interviews people from all walks of life about their relationship with creativity.
service_provided: private coaching, seminars in writing, bodhran, creativity and well-being, podcast host
